24
00:25:07,704 --> 00:25:14,704
9S: Say, 2B? Don't you think this white flower would look good on you?

25
00:25:14,728 --> 00:25:15,928
2B: I have no need for it.

26
00:25:16,052 --> 00:25:17,252
9S: Aw, are you sure?

27
00:25:17,276 --> 00:25:21,676
2B: Attaching a plant to my hair would do nothing for my combat abilities.

28
00:25:21,700 --> 00:25:25,000
 Rather, it would more likely cause maintenance failure.

29
00:25:25,024 --> 00:25:28,624
9S: Hahah. Man, 2B, you're way too serious, you know that?

30
00:25:30,448 --> 00:25:37,048
2B : I made a promise with 9S in the past.

31
00:25:38,272 --> 00:25:44,172
A promise that I'd continue to kill him, without fail.

32
00:25:44,896 --> 00:25:50,596
The 9S from back then, and the 9S before me are two different people.

33
00:25:51,020 --> 00:25:55,220
That fact ... makes my chest tighten.

34
00:25:56,644 --> 00:26:00,544
Pod 042: Pod 042 to YoRHa unit 2B.

35
00:26:00,568 --> 00:26:08,668
Report: Detecting errors occurring within unit 2B's memory
region, likely due to unstable psychological state.

36
00:26:09,092 --> 00:26:14,492
Proposal: Moderate rest should cause improvement.

37
00:26:15,216 --> 00:26:19,316
2B: I've already been aware of that for a long time ...

38
00:26:19,940 --> 00:26:26,940
