60
00:43:15,708 --> 00:43:19,008
Pod 042: Confirming the annihilation of all machine lifeforms in this area.

61
00:43:19,032 --> 00:43:20,432
9S: Whew ...

62
00:43:20,456 --> 00:43:23,856
2B: So we've destroyed every machine lifeform here?

63
00:43:23,880 --> 00:43:28,880
Pod 042: Affirmative: No responses from any machine lifeforms in this area.

64
00:43:28,904 --> 00:43:30,404
2B: Understood.

65
00:43:30,728 --> 00:43:35,628
9S: Huh? Hey, 2B ... did something happen to your right hand?

66
00:43:35,652 --> 00:43:41,952
2B: My right hand ...? Oh, this. I must've injured my finger during the previous battle.

67
00:43:41,976 --> 00:43:44,576
9S: Gah! You're — You're bleeding!

68
00:43:44,600 --> 00:43:48,200
Pod! Get me staunching gel and logic-virus vaccines! Then — uh —

69
00:43:48,224 --> 00:43:53,724
Pod 042: Inadvisable. There is a high probability that excessive
treatment will cause a decrease in movement efficiency to the unit ...

70
00:43:53,748 --> 00:43:55,748
9S: Just shut up and do it already!

71
