Pod 042: Large-scale attack ended in failure. The Bunker has collapsed.

93
00:59:22,624 --> 00:59:31,024
Black-box signal for YoRHa unit 2B offline. Death confirmed.

94
00:59:32,248 --> 00:59:38,848
A large "tower" produced by machine lifeforms rose within the city ruins.

95
00:59:40,272 --> 00:59:48,072
Having lost a place to return to, unit 9S aimed
for nothing more than the top of that "tower".

96
00:59:49,296 --> 00:59:55,296
In order to destroy the machine lifeforms which caused this nightmare.

97
00:59:55,520 --> 01:00:00,820
And to end himself as well.

98
01:00:02,344 --> 01:00:04,344


