Pod 042: Those memories are his greatest treasure.

107
01:01:02,863 --> 01:01:05,830
Living together, fighting together.

108
01:01:06,802 --> 01:01:11,002
They were like a family.

109
01:01:12,314 --> 01:01:14,914
9S: 2B ...

110
01:01:15,112 --> 01:01:21,812
Pod 042: 9S holds that recording deep within his heart.

111
01:01:22,317 --> 01:01:27,384
Treating it as if it were truly a treasure.

112
01:01:27,987 --> 01:01:35,587
9S: 2B ... I ... I'll be with you before long ...

113
01:01:35,611 --> 01:01:39,411
Pod 042: Reality and fiction blend together.

114
01:01:39,923 --> 01:01:47,223
With clouded consciousness, unit 9S carries himself forward, his legs heavy.

115
01:01:47,847 --> 01:01:51,847
He'll defeat as many enemies as possible, even if he is alone.

116
01:01:52,171 --> 01:01:57,871
As if in response to that wish, a new enemy appears.

117
01:02:00,595 --> 01:02:04,695
Many enemies appear in front of him.

118
01:02:04,919 --> 01:02:08,719
They're ... androids.

119
01:02:08,743 --> 01:02:13,143
They're ... YoRHa units.

120
01:02:13,400 --> 01:02:14,900
9S: 2B models?

121
01:02:15,724 --> 01:02:21,124
Pod 042: The person he treasures above all else.

122
01:02:21,362 --> 01:02:25,895
Someone who resides in a location out of his reach.

123
01:02:35,074 --> 01:02:42,241
I'm glad I got to see you here. I truly am.

124
01:02:44,065 --> 01:02:50,165
I'll tear you apart ... Every last one of you!

125
01:02:50,692 --> 01:02:54,592
Pod 042: 9S draws his sword.

126
01:02:54,803 --> 01:03:06,603
Pod 042: Is this an act of murderous intent? Or is it
perhaps done out of love? It's no longer possible to tell.

127
