Nearly 80% of his memory is contaminated, and his thought circuits are severely damaged.

129
01:23:53,282 --> 01:23:57,282
9S: Dammit ... I can't ... remove ...

130
01:23:57,506 --> 01:24:02,006
The vaccine ... it'll no longer ...

131
