To throw away all of his current memories, and be reborn anew.

134
01:24:23,949 --> 01:24:27,482
9S: No !... I can't do that ...

135
01:24:27,506 --> 01:24:35,206
No matter how contaminated I become ... I can't lose this memory ...

136
