142
01:25:12,474 --> 01:25:20,574
So ... please ... don't take them from me ...

143
01:25:22,429 --> 01:25:29,296
Pod 042: To him, calling her his family was much too silly.

144
01:25:30,289 --> 01:25:34,422
But calling her his lover was much too distant.

145
01:25:34,447 --> 01:25:43,580
9S: Machines ... A2 ... It doesn't matter ... I'll kill every last one of you!

146
01:25:44,311 --> 01:25:47,411
2B ...

147
01:25:47,944 --> 01:25:49,644
 I ...

148
01:25:52,742 --> 01:25:56,575
Pod 042: Within the corners of his eroding consciousness,

149
