9S continues to protect his memories of 2B.

150
01:26:04,031 --> 01:26:13,198
Even if ... his actions are completely meaningless in the eyes of the world.

151
01:26:15,570 --> 01:26:20,970
2B: I am ... No.2 ... Type E.

152
01:26:21,830 --> 01:26:27,863
I was created to execute my fellow YoRHa soldiers.

153
01:26:28,365 --> 01:26:30,365
9S: I'd already ...

154
01:26:31,427 --> 01:26:36,760
I'd already realized that ...

155
01:26:37,224 --> 01:26:41,891
2B: The mission I had been assigned over and over again...

156
01:26:43,004 --> 01:26:47,437
