157
01:26:47,880 --> 01:26:54,413
9S: Stop it ... Enough already ... 2B.

158
01:26:55,737 --> 01:27:01,304
Even if you were trying to kill me, I ...

159
01:27:01,453 --> 01:27:08,253
Being with you, it truly ...

