01:27:10,310 --> 01:27:15,410
... It felt like I'd found a family.

161
01:27:18,304 --> 01:27:22,604
2B: Hey ... 9S?

162
01:27:24,064 --> 01:27:29,597
I wonder ... Were the choices we made wrong?

163
01:27:33,880 --> 01:27:36,747
Pod 042: Within a pure white tower.

164
01:27:37,371 --> 01:27:40,571
A small boy walks.

165
01:27:41,590 --> 01:27:45,823
Suffering. Uneasy.

166
01:27:47,465 --> 01:27:54,232
Holding within him many small, important memories.

167
01:27:55,271 --> 01:28:01,038
They're of ... the time the two of them spent together.

168
01:28:03,191 --> 01:28:10,224
His memories of those days ... were most precious to him.

